(22, 'Asus Chromebook C434, 14” 2-in-1 laptop', 'Asus', 'The Asus Chromebook Flip C434 14 ”2-in-1 laptop has an elegant quality design that you can take with you on the go. The computer is designed with a focus on portability with the 1.57 cm thin profile and the weight of only 1.45 kg. And the fully rotating Full HD touch screen hinge ensures even more versatility when you want to share content with colleagues or just enjoy multimedia in tablet mode.\r\n\r\nGoogle Chrome OS\r\nThere are many usable installed Google applications like Docs, Maps, Gmail, Pics and more - with millions more available online in the Google Play Store. The operating system excels with easy setup and automatic updates every 6 weeks for maximum user comfort and security.\r\n\r\nProcessor and graphics card\r\nThe computer has an Intel Core M3-8100Y dual core processor from the Amber Lake Y family that has a power consumption of just 4.5 W. With the on-demand turbo mode, the device is ready to run even very demanding apps and multimedia. It is followed by 8GB of LPDDR3 RAM and onboard Intel UHD Graphics 615.\r\n\r\nFull HD touch screen The\r\n14 \"IPS LED WideView touch screen has crystal clear and detailed Full HD 1080p resolution. The touch recognition lets you control the device like a tablet, ideal for reviewing photos or zoom in and out of the map. IPS technology ensures deeper contrast, brighter colors and wider viewing angles.\r\n\r\nLightweight and portable\r\nwith only 1.57 cm thickness and 1.45 kg weight suits Chromebook fit easily in your travel bag, backpack or suitcase.\r\n\r\n2-in -1-form\r\nThe best from laptops and tablets in one package. You can rotate the screen to switch between standard computer mode if you need to type and want easy touch control for multimedia. Turn the keyboard back and watch movies, play touch games or give amazing animated presentations.\r\n\r\nStorage\r\nThe fast 64 GB flash drive ensures smooth and fast boot of the operating system and applications in just a few seconds. You can also use 100 GB Google Drive cloud storage for 1 year for free.\r\n\r\nConnectivity\r\n- 2x reversible USB 3.0 ports\r\n- 1x full-sized USB 3.0\r\n- Fast wi-fi ac, Bluetooth 4.0\r\n- Micro SD memory card port\r\n- 3.5mm mini audio jack\r\n\r\nOther features\r\n- Integrated webcam with 720p HD resolution\r\n- Touchpad with multitouch\r\n- Backlit keyboard\r\n- 3-cell lithium-polymer battery with 48 WHr capacity', 6, 3499, '2021-12-15 00:04:32', '2021-12-15 00:04:32', 1),
(23, 'Samsung T35F 24\" monitor', 'Samsung', 'This Samsung T35F 24 \"monitor is easy to use and delivers a sharp and detailed image in a beautiful, frameless design. The monitor has Full HD resolution with a frame rate of 75 Hz and a response time of 5 ms, which ensures a 100% fluid image , which is further enhanced by AMD FreeSync technology. You just need to plug in the HDMI cable and let yourself enjoy the sharp and vivid images.\r\n\r\nFull HD IPS panel The\r\n24 \"IPS panel delivers a sharp Full HD 1080p resolution with a high level of detail. IPS technology ensures deeper contrasts, clearer colors and wider viewing angles.\r\n\r\nAMD FreeSync\r\nThis technology synchronizes the screen refresh rate with one of your graphics cards, minimizing delays, screen tearing and lag. You can therefore enjoy a crisp and fluid movement, no matter what.\r\n\r\nKey features:\r\n- 24 \"/ 60.96 cm diagonal IPS LED panel\r\n- Max. Supported resolution: 1920 x 1080\r\n- 16: 9 screen format\r\n- 1,000: 1 static contrast\r\n- 5 ms response time\r\n- 250 nit brightness\r\n\r\nConnection:\r\n- 1x HDMI 1.4 port\r\n- 1X VGA port\r\n\r\nErgonomics:\r\n- 178 ° / 178 ° viewing angle\r\n- 20 ° / -2 ° screen tilt\r\n- 100 x 100 VESA brackets for wall mounting\r\n\r\nIncluded in the package:\r\n- HDMI cable\r\n- Power cable', 7, 799, '2021-12-15 00:25:21', '2021-12-15 00:25:21', 1),
(24, 'Lenovo G24-10 24\" gaming monitor', 'Lenovo', 'Enjoy your gaming to the fullest with the Lenovo G24-10 24 \"gaming screen. With its 24\" 144 Hz panel, you can immerse yourself in games and experience great performance. The screen follows when every millisecond counts. The excellent performance, the almost borderless screen and the beautiful stand fit the screen to your gamer table.\r\n\r\nUpdate speed\r\nWith the 144 Hz TN panel, you get near-instant input. It\'s good for gamers where every millisecond counts.\r\n\r\nKey functions:\r\n- 24 ”TN LED panel\r\n- Max. supported resolution: 1920 x 1080\r\n- 16: 9 screen ratio\r\n- 1,000: 1 static contrast\r\n- 3,000,000: 1 dynamic contrast\r\n- 1 ms response time (extreme)\r\n- 300 nit clarity\r\n\r\nConnections:\r\n- 1x HDMI 2.0\r\n- 1X DisplayPort 1.4\r\n- 1x 3.5 mm audio jack\r\n\r\nErgonomics:\r\n-\r\n170/160 ° viewing angle - 22 ° / -5 ° screen tilt\r\n- 100 x 100 VESA wall mounting standard\r\n- TUV Eye Comfort certified\r\n\r\nIncluded in the package:\r\n- HDMI cable\r\n- Power cord', 7, 1099, '2021-12-15 00:25:21', '2021-12-15 00:25:21', 1);
